YS TBG II LLC $1,535,000 Financing
YS TBG II LLC just submitted form D announcing $1,535,000 equity financing.  This is a new filing. YS TBG II LLC was able to sell $1,535,000. That is 100% of the round of financing. The total private offering amount was $1,535,000. The financing was made by 92 investors. Minimal accepted investment was $10,000. The financing document was filed on 2016-12-29. YS TBG II LLC is based in  229 W. 43RD STREET, 8TH FLOOR  NEW YORK 10036. The firm's business is Pooled Investment Fund. The firm's revenue range is Decline to Disclose. The form was signed by  Milind Mehere.





